    "• If applicable, the authors should discuss possible limitations of their approach to address problems of privacy and fairness.",
    "• While the authors might fear that complete honesty about limitations might be used by reviewers as grounds for rejection, a worse outcome might be that reviewers discover limitations that aren't acknowledged in the paper.",
    "The authors should use their best judgment and recognize that individual actions in favor of transparency play an important role in developing norms that preserve the integrity of the community.",
    "Reviewers will be specifically instructed to not penalize honesty concerning limitations.",
